*** '''Cecilia:''' Found it! Here you go.
*** {{tbox|pic=Secret santa present (2021 Christmas event, red) detail.png|Cecilia hands you the present.}}
*** '''Cecilia:''' Good luck, try not to lose them again!
** {{tact|end}}
